<body lang=3D"SV" link=3D"#0563C1" vlink=3D"#954F72" style=3D"word-wrap:bre=
ak-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Dear friends, <o:p></o:p></span=
></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">My best greetings from a winter=
y Stockholm. I hope this finds you all well and healthy, and that you have =
had good weeks since many of us last met! I realize it has already been a f=
ew weeks since we left our last meeting,
 and I apologize for not being in touch sooner!<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">First and foremost, a big thank=
s to all of you who were part of the last meeting. The meeting of course wa=
s not without its challenges, but I am still very glad that we could meet i=
n the way that we did, for the discussions
 shared, and for the plans made. Thank you!<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">As the year is now quickly comi=
ng to an end, I am writing to share some words of thanks, some updates abou=
t 2025 and some specific questions following our last meeting, connected to=
 a shared newsletter<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><u><span lang=3D"EN-US">Thank you<o:p></o:p></spa=
n></u></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">You have heard me say this many=
 times this year, and I will do it again: thank you! It has been a challeng=
ing year in a lot of ways, big and small, and some of those challenges has =
meant uncertainties for the future of
 our shared work. It has required patience and a lot of flexibility from al=
l of you and I very much appreciate how you have all showed this during the=
 year! Again, thank you!
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><u><span lang=3D"EN-US">2025<o:p></o:p></span></u=
></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><u><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p><span style=3D"text-=
decoration:none">&nbsp;</span></o:p></span></u></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">As we look ahead to 2025, we do=
 it with a lot more clarity and certainty than we have had in this last yea=
r. We know that a fourth cohort will start their journey with us shortly, w=
e know that there will be various shared
 projects and initiatives going forward, and thanks to the work we did toge=
ther in our meeting, we also have good ideas about how we best use the netw=
ork going forward. I will elaborate on one of these forward actions below =
=96 the idea of a monthly newsletter
 - and then I will be in touch about other activities and actions in the co=
ming weeks. The aim is that at the time of our next regular online meeting,=
 which will take place towards the end of January, we will have a presentat=
ion of what the whole year of 2025
 will entail for the network. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><u><span lang=3D"EN-US">Newsletter<o:p></o:p></sp=
an></u></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><u><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p><span style=3D"text-=
decoration:none">&nbsp;</span></o:p></span></u></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">During our last meeting, one of=
 the ideas discussed was to begin producing a monthly newsletter. A big tha=
nks to Ghaylen, Cheima and Abdi for capturing this idea and summarizing it =
in writing! Please read through the
 next part and answer the questions at the bottom.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">The idea of the newsletter was =
that it will be issued once a month, focused on the following topics:
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0cm;mso-list:l1 level1 =
lfo1"><span lang=3D"EN-US">The State of Human Rights: An overview of the ge=
neral situation regarding human rights in the region.<o:p></o:p></span></li=
></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoListParagraph"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span>=
</p>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"2" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0cm;mso-list:l1 level1 =
lfo1"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Existing Violations in Each Area: A detailed loo=
k at human rights violations specific to each subregion.<o:p></o:p></span><=
/li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoListParagraph"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span>=
</p>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"3" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0cm;mso-list:l1 level1 =
lfo1"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Latest Developments in Each Country Represented =
by Network Members: Updates on human rights events and progress in countrie=
s where network members are active.<o:p></o:p></span></li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoListParagraph"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span>=
</p>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"4" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0cm;mso-list:l1 level1 =
lfo1"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Raising Awareness in the Field of Human Rights: =
Topics include digital protection, physical protection, and the definition =
of key concepts.<o:p></o:p></span></li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoListParagraph"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span>=
</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Initially, this will start as a=
n internal newsletter for activists within the network. Once sustainability=
 and commitment are confirmed, the project can be expanded to include polic=
y briefs aimed at human rights organizations
 and decision-makers<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">For next steps, the following h=
as been proposed:
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0cm;mso-list:l0 level1 =
lfo2"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Drafting a Code of Conduct<o:p></o:p></span></li=
><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0cm;mso-list:l0 level1=
 lfo2"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Establishing a framework to guide the process.<=
o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0=
cm;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Preparing the Technical As=
pects of the Newsletter:<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagrap=
h" style=3D"margin-left:0cm;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2"><span lang=3D"EN-US">E=
nsuring all necessary resources and tools are in place.<o:p></o:p></span></=
li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0cm;mso-list:l0 leve=
l1 lfo2"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Appointing a Coordinator for Each Country<o:p=
></o:p></span></li><ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"1" type=3D"a">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0cm;mso-list:l0 level2 =
lfo2"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Each country will have a representative from the=
 network members.<o:p></o:p></span></li></ol>
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0cm;mso-list:l0 level1 =
lfo2"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Rotating Responsibility for Writing Each Month:<=
o:p></o:p></span></li><ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"1" type=3D"a">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0cm;mso-list:l0 level2 =
lfo2"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Every month, one network member will take charge=
 of authoring the content.<o:p></o:p></span></li></ol>
</ol>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b>=
</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US">In terms of taking this forw=
ard, please get back to me with the following:
<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b>=
</p>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0cm;mso-list:l2 level1 =
lfo3"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US">Are you interested in receiving should a mont=
hly newsletter?
<o:p></o:p></span></b></li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoListParagraph"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></sp=
an></b></p>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"2" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0cm;mso-list:l2 level1 =
lfo3"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US">Are you interested and willing to be the coor=
dinator for your country?
<o:p></o:p></span></b></li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoListParagraph"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></sp=
an></b></p>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"3" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0cm;mso-list:l2 level1 =
lfo3"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US">Are you interested and willing to be part of =
the rotating responsibility of writing each month?
<o:p></o:p></span></b></li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoListParagraph"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span>=
</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Again, I will be in touch with =
more updates and questions about the next year in the coming weeks. In the =
meantime, I wish you all a restful time as the year comes to an end, a happ=
y new year, and a good start to 2025!<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">My very best, <o:p></o:p></span=
></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Erik<o:p></o:p></span></p>
